OBJECTIVE  
Detail-oriented and proactive logistics professional with an Advanced Diploma in Logistics & Supply Chain 
Management. Seeking an entry-level position in a dynamic organization to apply knowledge of international 
logistics, warehousing, and transportation management. Proficient in SAP MM and MS Excel, with a solid 
foundation in handling exports, imports, and international trade operations. Committed to optimizing supply 
chain efficiency and contributing to seamless global operations.
